<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2048] Omit positions but keep termFreq</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2048</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;it would be useful to have an option to discard positional information but still keep the term frequency - currently setOmitTermFreqAndPositions discards both. Even though position-dependent queries wouldn&apos;t work in such case, still any other queries would work fine and we would get the right scoring.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
